    "Html": "\r\n<p>Change Set: greatmaps_f93232fdfe6f, Files: GMap.NET.WindowsPresentation\\GMap.NET.WindowsPresentation\\GMapControl.cs, Line: 169</p>\r\n<p>Was:</p>\r\n<p>double scaleValue = remainder &#43; 1;</p>\r\n<p>The relationship between zoom and resolution is not linear. Each time zoom is incremented by 1, resolution (m/pix) is halved.</p>\r\n<p>Should be:</p>\r\n<p>double scaleValue = Math.Pow(2d, remainder);</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Agree?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Great project. Thanks.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#008000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#008000; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; color:#008000; font-size:x-small\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n",
